@startuml patient_state
!theme plain
title Patient State Chart Diagram

[*] --> Initial

Initial --> Registered : register()\n[Reception creates patient record]

Registered --> Referred : refer()\n[General Doctor refers to specialist]

Referred --> XRayRequested : createXRayRequest()\n[Specialist Doctor creates X-ray request]

XRayRequested --> XRayProcessing : uploadImage()\n[Technician uploads X-ray image]

XRayProcessing --> ResultsAvailable : analyzeComplete()\n[AI analysis completes]

ResultsAvailable --> Completed : reviewResults()\n[Doctor reviews results]

' Self-transitions for additional requests
Referred --> Referred : createAdditionalXRayRequest()\n[Multiple X-ray requests possible]
ResultsAvailable --> XRayRequested : requestAnotherXRay()\n[Doctor requests additional X-ray]

' Error states
XRayProcessing --> XRayRequested : processingFailed()\n[Invalid image or processing error]

' Notes
note right of Registered
  Patient awaits triage by
  General Doctor
end note

note right of Referred
  Patient assigned to
  Specialist Doctor
end note

note right of XRayRequested
  X-ray examination
  order created
end note

note right of XRayProcessing
  AI analyzing chest X-ray
  for cardiomegaly detection
end note

note right of ResultsAvailable
  AI prediction and confidence
  score available for review
end note

note right of Completed
  Case assessment complete
  (may have multiple X-rays)
end note

@enduml